<paragraph id="9F8537AB6AB9E7E8B86AFCB6B6C71AA0" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A53FB83F8E868554895F98AB2F394199" pageId="0" pageNumber="117">China: Hainan: five males and one female, Baoting County, 2013.V.2, coll. Yan Shi and Shun-Hua Gui; three males, Changjiang County, Qicha Township, 2015.IV.28, coll. Lu Qiu and Qi-Kun Bai; one male and two females, Sanya City, Liupan Village, 2015.IV.8, coll. Lu Qiu and Qi-Kun Bai; two males (holotype and paratype), Baoting County, 1959.VII.10, coll. Yi-Chuan Hu. China: Guangxi: one male (paratype), Mt. Daqingshan, 1958.IX, coll. Yi-Xin Xu.</paragraph>
